subject: Wrestling
College Athletics
lead_paragraph: Top-ranked Iowa relied on a deep roster to take its second straight N.C.A.A. wrestling title Saturday night in St. Louis, sewing up its 22nd championship without winning a weight class and losing a point to penalty.
